Phase 6 is complete. Here's a summary of what was done:

## Package split

`main.go` (879 lines) was refactored into:

```
internal/config/config.go    — Config, ModelPrice, Load, EnsureFile, ExpandHome
internal/stats/types.go      — Session, HistoryEntry, StatuslineState
internal/stats/session.go    — CacheBase, LoadSession, SaveSession, ApplyTokens
internal/stats/history.go    — AppendHistory, ReadHistory
internal/stats/statusline.go — WriteStatusline, CostUSD, ExtractModel, StatuslinePath
internal/proxy/handler.go    — SSEInspector, Handler (callback-based)
internal/cli/stats.go        — all 5 CLI commands + formatting utils
main.go                      — type aliases + forwarding wrappers + graceful shutdown
```

`main_test.go` required **zero changes** — type aliases (`Session = stats.Session`, etc.) and forwarding functions keep all existing test call sites valid.

## Error handling audit

Silent `_ =` discards on I/O paths now `log.Printf` and continue. The `io.ReadAll` error in the proxy hot path now returns HTTP 400. No `log.Fatal` exists outside `main()`.

## Graceful shutdown

SIGINT/SIGTERM → `srv.Shutdown(5s ctx)` → `wg.Wait()` flushes in-flight `recordTokens` goroutines before exit.

## Benchmarks

| Benchmark | Result |
|---|---|
| ProxyHandler (loopback) | 118 µs/op |
| RecordTokens (disk I/O) | 121 µs/op |
| SSEInspector overhead | 5.5 µs vs 34 ns raw copy |
